{"tid":930012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"80後土瓜灣開免費午膳餐廳任食任裝","createTime":"2018-12-06T04:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T06:47:34.000Z","uid":1886,"like":32,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"cd540a64aff3bbcc903285295c671c058db91b0a","tid":930012,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:01:10.000Z","msg":"世上真的有免費午餐！28歲的寶善老師1年前於土瓜灣創立「感恩免費素食餐廳」（下稱感恩），讓有需要人士可舒舒服服、有尊嚴地坐在餐廳內享用免費午膳。開業一年，由被人看扁到獲街坊支持，「感恩」一直低調並以實際行動為社區出力，溫暖土瓜灣社區。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2220000/2220565/freemeal_thumb_20181130_S_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2220000%2F2220565%2Ffreemeal_thumb_20181130_S_600.jpg&h=7581163b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n寶善老師指起初成立「感恩」是不被看好的，始終沒有人相信世上會有免費午餐。縱使家人朋友都支持他，但店舖附近的商戶、街坊就覺得他「好傻」、甚至直言：「你好快就會執啦！」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2220000/2220565/fain1128013_1024_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2220000%2F2220565%2Ffain1128013_1024_600.jpg&h=7a6aa7de&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n雖然如此，「感恩」以行動證明理念是可行的。開業後1個月，不少街坊的態度已開始轉變，由原本抱著懷疑的心態入店進食，到被「感恩」的溫暖行動所說服。最明顯是，當「感恩」的義工去買菜時，商戶會主動送贈少量蔬菜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2220565/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2220565%2F&d=25lWIakmnjXfrruxfuQJpfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=31df24ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2220565/</a>"},{"pid":"dbe5fd92cd3dcd70100d438c8850af8579319ef0","tid":930012,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:03:28.000Z","msg":"當初選址土瓜灣，全因該區多「夾心階層」長者。當大家想到土瓜灣的長者大多持有物業，但寶善老師則留意到他們大多是持舊樓物業，一方面無法申領綜援和享受社會福利，另一方面舊樓危機處處，隨時要支付高昂維修費。這些長者在沒有收入又擔心突然患上大病的情況下，只能「死慳死抵」，甚至執紙皮幫補生活。"},{"pid":"b8e4c0e9654636cf4e53eb4ddc2ba6b1f4c7f20b","tid":930012,"uid":1886,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:05:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2220000/2220565/fain1128004_1024_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2220000%2F2220565%2Ffain1128004_1024_600.jpg&h=b5aa6d74&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n「感恩」店舖雖小，卻充滿人情味。店內除了有大廚、店長和兩位幫工，其他職員都是義工。他們每日早上8、9點就會開始準備餸菜，10點半左右開始派籌，11點開始招呼客人。「感恩」每日都會製作200份「3餸1湯、白飯任裝」的無味精、少油少鹽健康午餐。不要以為素菜味道一定普通，大廚華哥可是每日都會精心構思新菜式，盡量數個月內都不重複，保留新鮮感。<br />\n<br />\n不知不覺，「感恩」由最初勉強經營4個月，到現在已支撐了一年。正所謂英雄莫問出處，「感恩」同樣不會深究每位食客背後的故事，只要你有需要，任何人都可以入內吃免費午膳。不過眾多食客中亦有令寶善老師特別深刻的。<br />\n<br />\n秉承「白飯任裝」原則，「感恩」每日都會有1名食客吃6碗飯，原來該名食客是因為在外「吃不飽」才會每日到「感恩」吃6碗飯。雖然這食量有點誇張，但「感恩」沒有拒絕過他，義工更會主動每次多添一倍的飯量。"},{"pid":"fbcb85bb1a8983bd9c5e5ce56f86f8b35b4c1f46","tid":930012,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:08:21.000Z","msg":"亲"},{"pid":"b581423d057179b5a83f3fa5caa76a9bb46a8d33","tid":930012,"uid":23560,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:11:11.000Z","msg":"如果換著係班支那人實當係麥當勞咁坐係到打躉狂食<br />\n就算食唔晒都會照要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30807a3da2c07053b24ad13517d9d18cc4e3d179","tid":930012,"uid":4917,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:13:18.000Z","msg":"叫班支那人去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964c0910d1aad826f95424bb34c6633876ed635e","tid":930012,"uid":34409,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"好心唔好吹捧呢D 餐廳啦~~你咁樣「公告天下」實俾人食窮佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c950900feb9dc50633d34ea613bb2778af95716a","tid":930012,"uid":100772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"全場廢老"},{"pid":"62acd111db7b2bbe7c727ac9fd3c1d38cf9616e0","tid":930012,"uid":122134,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:20:44.000Z","msg":"靠咩生存到而家"},{"pid":"a33bac6254724a8c5fe8ee9463ee1ba4dcc1b796","tid":930012,"uid":51436,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:20:46.000Z","msg":"好快汁粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e7f039bf22aab58ae15a3ff1a910a830977258","tid":930012,"uid":1886,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tu9YMQw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftu9YMQw.png&h=5eb0e197&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d209644c4a93c53f555c2d6d663499b59cb144c","tid":930012,"uid":1886,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"964c0910d1aad826f95424bb34c6633876ed635e","tid":930012,"uid":34409,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"好心唔好吹捧呢D 餐廳啦~~你咁樣「公告天下」實俾人食窮佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:23:55.000Z","msg":"或許有人會擔心餐廳有很多貪心、佔便宜的食客，但意外地很多長者用膳後都會主動投放十元八款至捐款箱。記者訪問了2位每日到「感恩」吃飯的長者，他們表示每次會放下數元甚至20元，因為不想「白食」：「這是應該的，做人不可以這樣。吃了別人的飯菜總要「夾番多少」，這樣餐廳才會長久。」<br />\n<br />\n寶善老師指，其實最初不會有食客捐款，但慢慢他們會放下1元2元，正代表釋除貪念，成功啟發人心中的善。<br />\n<br />\n未來，他將繼續在社區送暖，先會在冬季派發超過1000張床墊予有需要人士，更計劃推行醫療車到舊區贈醫施藥。"},{"pid":"fe61d1f44e12edb4b0eed192ce8ed577482cac41","tid":930012,"uid":76776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:24:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97836565057caa07af82d14df1ec30a408b4c370","tid":930012,"uid":25073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"964c0910d1aad826f95424bb34c6633876ed635e","tid":930012,"uid":34409,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"好心唔好吹捧呢D 餐廳啦~~你咁樣「公告天下」實俾人食窮佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:24:52.000Z","msg":"素食嘅話應該得左膠會想食"},{"pid":"43088a57373f2e3051b01c91169653fcfe47c5bd","tid":930012,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:27:35.000Z","msg":"個老闆個樣咁鳩的呢"},{"pid":"2dc77aa136251d63bad72d5f0b42b744f97669d1","tid":930012,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30807a3da2c07053b24ad13517d9d18cc4e3d179","tid":930012,"uid":4917,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:13:18.000Z","msg":"叫班支那人去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:29:42.000Z","msg":"每一個人有他背後的故事，我們不深探，英雄莫問出處。人家不說、輕輕帶過，我們就知每一個人有難處。我們不標籤任何一個人，這亦是我們做地舖的原因。任何人都可以來食，不論貧富，只要你有需要就可以進來。"},{"pid":"5dfa68d2b3b5db53de7485ec43f2ca98e1c7a154","tid":930012,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:39:55.000Z","msg":"好似間野全場唔撚準出聲食飯"},{"pid":"6b1d9dd8e01c09176d3b7f0a0728122262313126","tid":930012,"uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5dfa68d2b3b5db53de7485ec43f2ca98e1c7a154","tid":930012,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:39:55.000Z","msg":"好似間野全場唔撚準出聲食飯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:42:39.000Z","msg":"俾人攪都唔可以出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394048acd6e5a624162557c11b659b5cb4c73635","tid":930012,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:43:04.000Z","msg":"小紅書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf289c61a1cc14c1dd3cc4a47d481d9305f59044","tid":930012,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:44:18.000Z","msg":"好快玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60e99edaf46812bbb8b70a51de4121f59d2f35f","tid":930012,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"964c0910d1aad826f95424bb34c6633876ed635e","tid":930012,"uid":34409,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"好心唔好吹捧呢D 餐廳啦~~你咁樣「公告天下」實俾人食窮佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:45:08.000Z","msg":"上報=自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44ca81ec32b44d7e0d8316309e31d4896497af7","tid":930012,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:45:12.000Z","msg":"好C君feel"},{"pid":"506c4feaa066835eb423e19fed8b450e7f803f39","tid":930012,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30807a3da2c07053b24ad13517d9d18cc4e3d179","tid":930012,"uid":4917,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:13:18.000Z","msg":"叫班支那人去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到時幾萬人逼爆成個土瓜灣"},{"pid":"a9722aad0dc5af968caffdfbf79a6f5054c24e85","tid":930012,"uid":81437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:48:11.000Z","msg":"次次11點拎行過都見到一排老人家排隊等食飯"},{"pid":"d3940331237a6bfd5d7ae6bb6ac45770a06a18dc","tid":930012,"uid":51387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:50:16.000Z","msg":"旅行團飯堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}